<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Manage pull requests</b></p><p>Manage incoming GitHub pull requests directly from IntelliJ IDEA: from the main menu select <span class="control">Git | GitHub | View Pull Requests</span>. IntelliJ IDEA lets you assign and merge pull requests, view the timeline and inline comments, submit comments and reviews, and accept changes without leaving the IDE.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_pull_requests.png" alt="Incoming pull requests" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>